com.habelitz.jsobjectizer.jsom.api.base
Interface CommonTypeTopLevelScope

All Superinterfaces:
JSOM
All Known Subinterfaces:
AbstractTypeTopLevelScope, AnnotationTopLevelScope, ClassTopLevelScope, InterfaceTopLevelScope
public interface CommonTypeTopLevelScope
extends JSOM

This JSOM type supports all those things that can exist within all kinds type declarations excepting enumeration types.

Author:
Dieter Habelitz

removeTypeMemberDeclaration

void removeTypeMemberDeclaration(TypeMemberDeclaration pTypeMemberDeclaration)
                                 throws JSourceObjectizerException
Removes a certain type member declaration from this.

Calling this method equals an removeTypeMemberDeclaration(TypeMemberDeclaration, true) call.

Parameters:
pTypeMemberDeclaration - The type member declaration that should be removed. The argument passed to this method remains unchanged.
Throws:
JSourceObjectizerException - if the type member declaration passed to this method doesn't belong to this.

removeTypeMemberDeclaration

void removeTypeMemberDeclaration(TypeMemberDeclaration pTypeMemberDeclaration,
                                 boolean pRemovingOfSurroundingHiddenTokensEnabled)
                                 throws JSourceObjectizerException
Removes a certain type member declaration from this.

Parameters:
pTypeMemberDeclaration - The type member declaration that should be removed. The argument passed to this method remains unchanged.
pRemovingOfSurroundingHiddenTokensEnabled - If true the method also tries to remove surrounding whitespaces and comments that most likely belongs to the type member declaration.
Throws:
JSourceObjectizerException - if the type member declaration passed to this method doesn't belong to this.
